\n|\n\n### notes.md\n\n| POC upload to github release  \n  \n## Repository files navigation\n\n# gcloud-lite CLI Distribution\n\nGoogle's gcloud CLI distribution is bloated with unnecessary dependencies\nincluding a complete python3 installation and large anthos binary. This\nresults in slower instance boot times, and costly storage & transfer fees\n\nGCloud-Lite is a distribution of the CLI that strips these unnessary\ndependencies to reduce the size by > 75%\n\n## Artifacts\n\n  * Runnable docker image \u2014 93% smaller\n  * tgz tarball \u2014 75% smaller\n\n## Running the Docker Image\n\n    \n    \n    $ docker pull us-west1-docker.pkg.dev/tonym-us/gcloud-lite/gcloud-lite # re-use existing credentials with -v $ docker run -v$HOME:/root us-west1-docker.pkg.dev/tonym-us/gcloud-lite/gcloud-lite compute instances list\n\n### Running ghutil, bq and other utilities\n\n    \n    \n    $ docker run -v$HOME:/root --entrypoint ghutil us-west1-docker.pkg.dev/tonym-us/gcloud-lite/gcloud-lite ARGS $ docker run -v$HOME:/root --entrypoint bq us-west1-docker.pkg.dev/tonym-us/gcloud-lite/gcloud-lite ARGS\n\n## Downloading gcloud-lite .tgz release\n\n    \n    \n    $ curl -LO https://github.com/tonymet/gcloud-lite/releases/download/472.0.0/google-cloud-cli-472.0.0-linux-x86_64-lite.tar.gz $ tar -zxf *gz\n\n## Discussions About gcloud CLI bloat\n\n  * GoogleCloudPlatform/gsutil#1732\n\n## About\n\nNo description, website, or topics provided.\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nGPL-3.0 license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n0 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases 2\n\n472.0.0 Latest\n\nApr 16, 2024\n\n\\+ 1 release\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Shell 57.2%\n  * Dockerfile 37.3%\n  * Makefile 5.5%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
